Privacy Policy for Word Hurdle - Word Game
Last updated: Dec 08 2023
Thank you for choosing Word Hurdle - Word Game ("us," "we," or "our"). This Privacy Policy is designed to help
                                you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile
                                application and services.
Information We Collect
Personal Information:
We may collect information that you provide to us, such as your
                                    name when you register or contact us for support.
Game Data:
We collect data related to your gameplay, scores, and achievements to enhance
                                    your gaming experience.
Device Information:
We may automatically collect information about your device,
                                    including device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for:
Providing Services:
To deliver and maintain our services, including game functionality,
                                    customer support, and personalized content.
Improving User Experience:
Analyzing user interactions to enhance and optimize our app's
                                    performance, features, and content.
Communication:
Sending you important updates, notifications, and responding to your
                                    inquiries.
Data Sharing and Security
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. Your data is stored
                                securely, and we take reasonable measures to protect it.
Third-Party Services
Our app may use third-party services such as analytics tools. These services may collect and process data in
                                accordance with their own privacy policies.
Premium features and Plans
Word Hurdle offers monthly and annual subscription options. Our “Monthly” subscription is paid in monthly instalments. For each month that your monthly subscription is active, you acknowledge and agree that Word Hurdle is authorized to charge the same credit card or other payment method (the “Payment Method”) as was used for the initial subscription fee in the amount of the then current monthly subscription fee. The monthly renewal subscription fees will continue to be billed to the Payment Method you provided, automatically until cancelled. You must cancel your subscription before it renews each month in order to avoid billing of the next month's subscription fee to the Payment Method you provided. Refunds cannot be claimed for any partial-month subscription period. You may discontinue auto-renewals of your subscription at any time by going to phone settings -> Account -> Subscriptions. Our “Yearly” subscription is paid in yearly instalments. For each year that your yearly subscription is active, you acknowledge and agree that Word Hurdle is authorized to charge the same credit card or other payment method (the “Payment Method”) as was used for the initial subscription fee in the amount of the then current yearly subscription fee. The yearly renewal subscription fees will continue to be billed to the Payment Method you provided, automatically until cancelled. You must cancel your subscription before it renews each year in order to avoid billing of the next year’s subscription fee to the Payment Method you provided. Refunds cannot be claimed for any partial-year subscription period. You may discontinue auto-renewals of your subscription at any time by going to phone settings -> Account -> Subscriptions. You are responsible for all applicable fees and charges incurred, including applicable taxes, and all subscriptions purchased by you. Our obligation to provide service is only valid once we have received payment. You agree not to hold us responsible for banking charges incurred due to payments on your account. We may at any time, in our sole discretion, change the fees and charges, or add new fees and charges, in relation to the Program or any services offered through the Program. If you do not agree to the change, you may cancel your membership or subscription in your account settings.
Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the date of
                                the last update will be modified accordingly.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
wordhurdle@hotmail.com
By using Word Hurdle - Word Game, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.